            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <p class="responsive-text">
        The project location is flexible, allowing students to choose a real site that meaningfully supports the intended spiritual condition. The selected location must be conceptually justified and demonstrate a clear relationship between site qualities, inner state, and architectural typology.

